    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A five eyed cat from space, a horde of gloopy shadow kittens, and a mystical twilight world await you in <strong>Outclaw</strong> - the debut minion management action adventure from Moss Monkey Games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/fba4081f4bd723ae234c58c82aa6d001.poster.avif?t=1772015644\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/fba4081f4bd723ae234c58c82aa6d001.webm?t=1772015644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AN ARMY OF CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Outclaw</strong>, you'll collect, command and control Shades - mischievous feline monsters with the ability to combine and transform into a variety of useful objects. From simple ramps and bridges to a giant pair of spectral arms or a grappling hook, anything is possible with an army of these little creatures at your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/ca1e07074cdd0e62de18767aa31a7265.poster.avif?t=1772015644\" width=616 height=231 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/ca1e07074cdd0e62de18767aa31a7265.webm?t=1772015644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHAPE YOUR SHADES </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your Shades into various useful constructs - stairs, boats, weapons and more. Make bigger, stronger forms by using multiple shades at once. Learn six freeform shapes you can place and upgrade wherever you want, and discover many others hidden around the world in secret locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/c35cbebfccb5c377a0bf0fd9b83d3d9e.poster.avif?t=1772015644\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/c35cbebfccb5c377a0bf0fd9b83d3d9e.webm?t=1772015644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRYSTALS, CONSTELLATIONS AND CATS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Giblet, a lost little cat from space searching for his family. Through him, you'll explore a variety of fantastical environments spread across 12 levels, from the crystal reef of the Inbetween to the gilded boughs of the Parliament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/6b7cfdcf8cca09111c279ccbd1523e18.poster.avif?t=1772015644\" width=616 height=293 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/6b7cfdcf8cca09111c279ccbd1523e18.webm?t=1772015644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD A FAMILY </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you go, amass an ever-growing horde of minions and companions, building out a home for yourself in a cosy, customisable hub world known as the Pavilion. Gather minions, treasure, hats, and all manner of shiny trinkets for your collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/b18f3f07277a99cc6c1463646ab742a2.poster.avif?t=1772015644\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165050/extras/b18f3f07277a99cc6c1463646ab742a2.webm?t=1772015644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GIVE THE LITTLE GUYS HATS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customise your minions with over 50 unique unlockable cosmetics, and countless combinations to really make your shades your own, then venture out into the stars with your favourite little freaks and unravel a magical story full of gods, monsters and mischief!</p>",
